Package: rapp.core.condition
Type: Package
Title: Custom R conditions
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2014-09-11
Author: Janko Thyson [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Janko Thyson <janko.thyson@gmail.com>
Description: Allows the creation of custom condition classes and thus the
    use of more complex/informative condition objects and messages.
    This package is a fundamental building block of the rapp framework
    and its associated higher level packages.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
NeedsCompilation: no
Repository: CRAN
